```vue
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-4">
  <!-- 内容 -->
</div>
```

### 生成按钮组件时
```vue
<button class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition-colors">
  按钮文本
</button>
```

